IF Statement : It is keyword in java.
Working :  
          1) An 'If' statements has condition with a block which contain the statements.
          2) The Condition must be a boolean types.
          3) IF the condition evaluate to true the statement of the 'if' block will exectue, if the condition evalute to flase then the if block will be skipped.
Syntax :
        if ( condition ) ; ---------->  must be a boolean type
          {
             //statements
          }
